long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Totally Awesome Roblox Extension (TARE) adds many quality of life improvements to the Roblox website, trying to be as visually integrated as possible.

These features include:

- Compressing the badge box into a grid, plus sorting and a progress bar for you completionists!
- Viewing the last server you joined, and rejoining it if it's still active! You can also hop into a random server too.
- Jumping directly to a creator's catalog, straight from an item page!
- Moving the Classic clothing section to the top of the avatar editor tabs, removing those pesky misclicks on layered clothing.


TARE is not affiliated with or endorsed by Roblox!
